M||tx|---
M||titl|Conditional md Loading
M||impa|hi
M||impa|loads large data only when needed
M||tags|bundle, conditional-loading, lazy-loading
M||tx|---
M|Cond|tx|Load large data or modules only when a feature is activated.
M|Cond|**Ex|**
M|Cond|tx|```tsx
M|Cond|func|{ enabled: boolean; setEnabled: rc.Dispatch<rc.SetStateAction<boolean>> }) {
M|Cond|tx|const [frames, setFrames] = useState<Frame[] \| null>(null)
M|Cond|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Cond|tx|if (enabled && !frames && typeof window !== 'undefined') {
M|Cond|tx|import('./animation-frames.js')
M|Cond|tx|.then(mod => setFrames(mod.frames))
M|Cond|tx|.catch(() => setEnabled(false))
M|Cond|tx|}
M|Cond|tx|}, [enabled, frames, setEnabled])
M|Cond|tx|if (!frames) return <Skeleton />
M|Cond|tx|return <Canvas frames={frames} />
M|Cond|tx|}
M|Cond|tx|```
M|Cond|tx|The `typeof window !== 'undefined'` check prevents bundling this md for SSR, optimizing server bundle size and bd speed.